---
title: Corn-ucopia Summer Chowder  with DIY Dill Biscuits
description: Indulge in the flavours of summer with our delightful corn chowder recipe, paired perfectly with biscuits packed with dill flavour. This creamy, comforting chowder features fresh, sweet corn kernels, tender chunks of sweet potatoes and a generous helping of chopped chives.
